name: helmrelease-ex

values.raw:
arch:
  amd64: 2 - No preference
  ppc64le: 2 - No preference
  s390x: 2 - No preference
autoscaling:
  enabled: false
  maxReplicas: 2
  metrics:
    cpu:
      targetAverageUtilization: 100m
  minReplicas: 1
image:
  pullPolicy: Always
  repository: ibmcom/icp-nodejs-sample
  tag: 10
livenessProbe:
  initialDelaySeconds: 30
  periodSeconds: 10
resources:
  limits:
    cpu: 100m
    memory: 128Mi
  requests:
    cpu: 100m
    memory: 128Mi
sch:
  global: {}
service:
  port: 3000
  type: NodePort

config.raw:
license: accept
selectedCluster:
  -
    label: local-cluster
    value: local-cluster
    ip: 9.30.161.147
    namespace: local-cluster
autoscaling:
  enabled: false

manifest:
---
# Source: ibm-nodejs-sample/templates/service.yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: helmrelease-ex-nodejssample-nodejs
  labels:
    app: "nodejsSample"
    chart: "ibm-nodejs-sample"
    heritage: "Tiller"
    release: "helmrelease-ex"
    component: "nodejs"
  annotations:
    prometheus.io/scrape: 'true'
spec:
  type: NodePort
  ports:
    - port: 3000
  selector:
    app: nodejsSample
    release: helmrelease-ex
    component: nodejs
---
# Source: ibm-nodejs-sample/templates/deployment.yaml
# Licensed Materials - Property of IBM
# (C) Copyright IBM Corp. 2018. All Rights Reserved.
# US Government Users Restricted Rights - Use, duplication or disclosure restricted by GSA ADP Schedule Contract with IBM Corp.
apiVersion: extensions/v1beta1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: "helmrelease-ex-nodejssample-nodejs"
  labels:
    app: "nodejsSample"
    chart: "ibm-nodejs-sample"
    heritage: "Tiller"
    release: "helmrelease-ex"
    component: "nodejs"
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      release: "helmrelease-ex"
  replicas: 1
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: "nodejsSample"
        chart: "ibm-nodejs-sample"
        heritage: "Tiller"
        release: "helmrelease-ex"
        component: "nodejs"
      # Here's where a user could define their own annotation too
      annotations:        
        productID: "Node.js_Sample_Application_2.0.0_perpetual_00000"
        productName: "Node.js Sample Application"
        productVersion: "2.0.0"
    spec:
      hostNetwork: false
      hostPID: false
      hostIPC: false
      securityContext:
        runAsNonRoot: true
        runAsUser: 1000
      affinity:        
        nodeAffinity:
          requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
            nodeSelectorTerms:
            - matchExpressions:
              - key: beta.kubernetes.io/arch
                operator: In
                values:
                - amd64
                - ppc64le
                - s390x
            
          preferredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
          - weight: 2
            preference:
              matchExpressions:
              - key: "beta.kubernetes.io/arch"
                operator: "In"
                values:
                - amd64
          - weight: 2
            preference:
              matchExpressions:
              - key: "beta.kubernetes.io/arch"
                operator: "In"
                values:
                - ppc64le
          - weight: 2
            preference:
              matchExpressions:
              - key: "beta.kubernetes.io/arch"
                operator: "In"
                values:
                - s390x
      containers:
      - name: ibm-nodejs-sample
        image: "ibmcom/icp-nodejs-sample:10"
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        securityContext:
          privileged: false
          readOnlyRootFilesystem: true
          allowPrivilegeEscalation: false
          runAsNonRoot: true
          runAsUser: 1000
          capabilities:
            drop:
            - ALL
        livenessProbe:
          httpGet:
            path: /health
            port: 3000
          initialDelaySeconds: 30
          periodSeconds: 10
        readinessProbe:
          httpGet:
            path: /health
            port: 3000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: "100m"
            memory: "128Mi"
          limits:
            cpu: "100m"
            memory: "128Mi"
        env:
          - name: PORT
            value : "3000"

        preference:
          matchExpressions:
          - key: "beta.kubernetes.io/arch"
